data.eml:eml: Orientatractis brycini sp. nov. (Nematoda: Atractidae) from characiform freshwater fishes in Gabon, Africa

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article David González-Solís, Jean Mariaux (2017): Orientatractis brycini sp. nov. (Nematoda: Atractidae) from characiform freshwater fishes in Gabon, Africa. Revue suisse de Zoologie 124 (1): 1-8, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.322659
